{
  "stem": "7093.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in between, I found-- I got into two choirs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I was a very good sight reader.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got into two choirs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I earned a bit of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I-- all that, I all did this, all this illegally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I earned a bit of money with that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then I tried my hand also at some sewing, but sewing by piece in a sweatshop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was hopeless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one day, I couldn't finish a shirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I earned absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and I came home crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, in between, I was eating in a canteen run by the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I also, there was a-- there was a possibility to get into the Sorbonne without certificates, to, to get into the Sorbonne, And I got in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I wanted to do psychopedagogy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, and I had to take another course, which was a secondary course, which was music aesthetics and appreciation-- not appreciation-- theory and aesthetics and criticism, music criticism also.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I got a job at the Hungarian house, writing out the addresses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But this job was from 2:00 to, to 12:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my course in psychopedagogy was in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I couldn't attend that course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I met-- I, I, I ate in this canteen, this joint canteen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I always heard people singing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so I wanted to join a choir.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I thought, well, I would love to sing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I didn't know it was a professional choir.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But anyway, I went in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I asked if I could get a audition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They would take me-- took me, they took me on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And, and then one day, there was no choir practice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And, and the, and, but, but I didn't-- and all the people didn't come.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
